column2: food_effect(foodlist = c("Apple juice","Apple juice + donut")) %>% group_by(experiment) %>% mutate(delta = (time - min(time))/60) %>% ggplot(aes(x=delta,y=value, color = experiment)) + geom_line(size = 2) + scale_x_continuous() + labs(title = "Glucose after apple juice", x = "Minutes", y = "mg/dL")
